---
lang: en
permalink: /offer/side-steps-running-boards/
title: Side Steps & Running Boards
description: Side steps and running boards for pickups and 4x4 vehicles - solid construction, easier access, and additional body protection.
category: Side Steps & Running Boards
---

<section class="pt-xlarge pb-xlarge products-category">
<div class="container">
  {% set breadcrumbHome = "Strona główna" %}
  {% set breadcrumbOffer = "Oferta" %}
  {% set breadcrumbOfferUrl = "/oferta/" %}
  {% if lang == "en" %}
  {% set breadcrumbHome = "Home" %}
  {% set breadcrumbOffer = "Offer" %}
  {% set breadcrumbOfferUrl = "/offer/" %}
  {% endif %}
  <nav class="breadcrumbs uppercase small color-accent-1">
    <a href="{{ langPrefix }}/">{{ breadcrumbHome }}</a>
    <span>|</span>
    <a href="{{ langPrefix }}{{ breadcrumbOfferUrl }}">{{ breadcrumbOffer }}</a>
    <span>|</span>
    <span>{{ title }}</span>
  </nav>
  <h1 class="xl split-lines color-light-1 mb-5 mt-3">{{ title }}</h1>

  {% set products = collections.productCategories[lang][category] | sortByOrder %}

  {% if products and products.length %}
    <div class="products-grid row g-3">
      {% for product in products %}
         <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3">
        <a href="{{ product.url | url }}">
        <article class="product-card rounded-md">
          {% productImage product.data.productImage, product.data.title %}
          <div class="product-card-content p-4 bg-light-1">
          <h3 class="h4 mt-0 line-clamp-3">{{ product.data.title }}</h3>
          <a href="{{ product.url | url }}" class="color-accent-1 small">Zobacz więcej &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        </a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <p>Brak produktów w tej kategorii.</p>
  {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>



<section class="cat-description pt-medium pb-large" id="opis">
  <div class="container"> 
    <div class="cat-desc-content bg-light-1 p-3 p-md-5 rounded-md">
      <div class="row g-5">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <div class="description-content">
          <h3>Side Steps</h3> <p> Durable Jusn side steps are a robust solution designed for off-road vehicles used in demanding conditions. Engineered for maximum functionality, they make it easier to get into the vehicle, access the roof rack, and improve everyday usability of cars equipped with a suspension lift. </p> <div class="line-x"></div> <p> The side steps are designed to provide maximum functionality in off-road conditions – their openwork construction reduces weight, makes it easier to clean off mud and snow, and prevents dirt from accumulating during off-road driving. </p> <div class="line-x"></div> <h3>Technology and Manufacturing</h3> <p> The product is manufactured using precise CNC machining, electroplating, and powder coating, ensuring high resistance to corrosion, mechanical damage, and harsh weather conditions. The mechanical design (no electronics) guarantees greater reliability compared to electric side steps, especially in off-road and expedition applications. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
         <div class="sticky">

         </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <video poster="/content/products/video/poster/progi-boczne.png" controls autoplay loop muted playsinline class="mt-5 rounded-md">
        <source src="/content/products/video/progi-boczne.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>










